POST /api/location/{ parentLocationId }     Request parameters   parentLocationId (string) - ID of parent location     Request body   name   test  type  geoLoc      Example Request   POST /api/location/582e2b2c065b2545ded3aabd HTTP/1.1
{
    "name":"CIC",
  "type":"BUILDING",
    "geoLoc": {
      "coordinates": [
        40.4509146,
        -79.9024777
      ]     
    }    
}   Example Response   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "_id": "5833479babdafd7b34858958",
    "name": "CIC",
    "test": false,
    "type":"BUILDING"
    "children": [
     {}
    ],
    "geoLoc": {
      "coordinates": [
        40.4509146,
        -79.9024777
      ],
      "type": "Point"
    }
}

Request URL   GET /api/location/{ locationId }    Request parameters  locationId (string) - ID of location to get.      Example Request   GET /api/location/582e2b2c065b2545ded3aabd HTTP/1.1   Example Response   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "_id": "582e2b2c065b2545ded3aabd",
    "name": "CMU",
    "test": false,
    "children": [
        "5833479babdafd7b34858958"
    ]
}

PUT /api/location/{ locationId }     Request parameters   locationId (string) - ID of location to update     Request body     name   test  type  geoLoc      Example Request   PUT /api/location/582e2b2c065b2545ded3aabd HTTP/1.1

{
    "name" : "CMU Campus"
}   Example Response   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
{
    "_id": "582e2b2c065b2545ded3aabd",
    "name": "CMU Campus",
    "test": false,
    "children": [
        "5833479babdafd7b34858958"
    ]
}

POST /api/gateway/    Request body    name   location_id  type  enabled  pubsub      Example Request   POST /api/gateway HTTP/1.1
{
    "name": "LabGateway",
    "location_id": "5833479babdafd7b34858958",
    "type": "LORA",
    "pubsub": {
      "protocol": "MQTT",
      "endpoint": "/gateways/LabGateway"
    } 
}   Example Response   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "_id": "5873dfefc653394e3f0966b9",
    "name": "LabGateway",
    "location_id": "5833479babdafd7b34858958",
    "type": "LORA",
    "__v": 0,
    "enabled": true,
    "pubsub": {
      "protocol": "MQTT",
      "endpoint": "/gateways/LabGateway"
    }  
}

PUT /api/gateway/{ gatewayId }     Request parameters   id (string) - ID of gateway to update     Request body     name   location_id  type  enabled  pubsub      Example Request   PUT /api/gateway/587e9cf0ee4cf540f8590784 HTTP/1.1

{
    "name" : "CICGateway_Lab"
}   Example Response   HTTP/1.1 200 OK
{
    "_id": "587e9cf0ee4cf540f8590784",
    "name": "CICGateway_Lab",
    "location_id": "5833479babdafd7b34858958",
    "type": "LORA",
    "__v": 0,
    "enabled": true,
    "pubsub": {
      "protocol": "MQTT",
      "endpoint": "/gateways/CICGateway"
    }
}
